timing_normal..._weight_factor(25.10)    timing_normal..._weight_factor(25.10)

Name
       timing_normalized_driver_waveform_weight_factor

Syntax
       timing_normalized_driver_waveform_weight_factor

       <<float value>>

       Default: 0.5

       Defines  the  value of the weight of linear components in the algorithm
       for generation of normalized driver waveform.

       When set to 1, the waveform will be purely linear. When set to  0,  the
       waveform  will be purely exponential. You can specify values within the
       range of 0 to 1.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

